748
00:55:30,151 --> 00:55:31,416
So-Jung!

749
00:55:32,694 --> 00:55:34,434
Aku merasa malu!

750
00:55:42,926 --> 00:55:44,670
Kenapa di saat seperti ini...

751
00:55:46,508 --> 00:55:47,314
Anakku, I-Na.

752
00:55:47,436 --> 00:55:49,458
Itu I-Na! Cepat angkat!

753
00:55:49,498 --> 00:55:51,122
Baiklah, mohon tunggu sebentar.

754
00:55:52,977 --> 00:55:54,688
Anakku! Kenapa?

755
00:55:55,822 --> 00:55:57,564
Cepat pulang dan makan bersama!

756
00:55:58,850 --> 00:55:59,900
Apa?

757
00:56:00,998 --> 00:56:02,231
Sedang bersama siapa?

758
00:56:05,033 --> 00:56:07,036
Baiklah. Ya sudah.

759
00:56:08,200 --> 00:56:09,117
Kenapa?

760
00:56:09,939 --> 00:56:11,767
Kita berdua saja.

761
00:56:13,484 --> 00:56:14,864
Aneh.

762
00:56:16,064 --> 00:56:18,580
