- Lalu kenapa?

764
00:56:21,450 --> 00:56:22,850
Ayah itu lajang!

765
00:56:23,448 --> 00:56:24,548
Apa ini?

766
00:56:25,146 --> 00:56:26,543
Aku begini karena Ibu!

767
00:56:26,820 --> 00:56:28,650
Ibu tidak ingin rujuk?

768
00:56:29,088 --> 00:56:30,151
Entahlah.

769
00:56:30,400 --> 00:56:32,227
Setelah Ibu coba pikirkan,

770
