777
00:57:02,041 --> 00:57:04,463
Itu pengalaman
terbaik di hidupku.

778
00:57:04,938 --> 00:57:06,257
Jantungku masih
berdegup kencang.

779
00:57:09,634 --> 00:57:11,034
Detektif Geum

780
00:57:16,046 --> 00:57:17,163
Siapa?

